column5: A buddy and I got out on the water saturday for some much needed fishing time !  We were fishing in about 8-10 ft of water, looking for some Northerns and ended up with their BIG cousin !!!!!  Never measured or weighed the girl, but Im guessing between 40-45 inches and we figured it was over 30 lbs. It was HEAVY !!!!!!!!      She took about 5 minutes to get her breath back, but swam away good and strong !  I noticed she left me a nice surprise on the boat.......     This is why I love fishing !!!!
Can't go wrong with a surprise 'ski!  Were you using heavy tackle for the pike?
A little ski-poo on the carpet eh!!  You'll have to get out the steam cleaner

beauty fish man! i dont think she is pushing 30 lbs at that length but 20 is probably a better estimate.  i dont want to take anything away from your fish because it is a beautiful muskie, no matter the weight you should be pumped!!  cheers dude
What a beautiful Ski.  She has now left her mark on your boat  Nice surprise for sure
Those aren't capri pants you're wearing are they? If they are, I don't care how big the muskie was, turn in your man card and your fishing license.  J/K - Nice Fish!!
hahah NOOO sir !!!!! They are on the long side of being shorts.... but also, they are a few sizes to big and like to fall off my   when I'm doing stufF  Thanks for the replies everyone !
A great looking fish. Congrats to you!
Nice fish man! great surprise for sure
Gorgeous ski man, congrats !!  Yep I've had them "poop" many times.  No problem, well worth it.
Well done man, beauty fish for sure!
Nice colors on her congrats Tyler
Nice fish for sure.  I don't think you should clean off that stuff. It's for good luck
Beautiful! Congrats
sweet surprise !
hahah I left it just as she left it !!!! Good luck stains !  Thanks for the replies everyone
nice ski for sure !!! cheers
Nice musky, always exciting to get into one of these monsters.
that's a real nice catch, congrats!
Love when that happens....congrats, a beauty!!
Nice Ski for sure. And you know the rules, them are Capri's hand in your man card and the capri's. I know a lady friend that would fit into those nicely.
THEY ARENT CAPRIS !!!!!! hahaha Thanks for the comments everyone
